race.description: Become A Brc Member Qtis 3YO Maiden Plate
race.comment: CRASH THE PARTY (11) has placed over this track and trip and will strip fitter second-up from the spell. Maps well from gate five and should be right there at the business end. The well-related EXCELBOOM (3) (half to G3 winner Shiki) has hit the top four in all three starts to date and this is not an overly strong affair. Top-three aspirations in a race decimated by scratchings. CELTIC BRAVE (2) ran a solid second at Ipswich on debut and will have taken a lot from that day at the races. In the mix. CARBONARA (10) will be at peak fitness now and can feature with any luck from the wide draw. DESANTO (12) next in line on debut.
